50|$|The President of <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> National <b>Authority</b> (رئيس السلطة الوطنية الفلسطينية) is {{the highest-ranking}} {{political}} position (equivalent to head of state) in <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> National <b>Authority</b> (PNA). <b>The</b> President appoints the Prime Minister of <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> National <b>Authority</b> from <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> Legislative Council, {{with whom he}} shares power.|$|R
