50|$|The Interior Ministry of <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> National <b>Authority</b> is <b>the</b> {{branch of}} <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> National <b>Authority</b> (PNA) cabinet {{in charge of}} the {{security}} and the statistics of the population of <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> National <b>Authority.</b> <b>The</b> <b>Palestinian</b> Central Bureau of Statistics (PCBS) is a sub-branch of the Interior Ministry that has the responsibility for the population and economic statistics of <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> territories. Since Hamas' takeover of Gaza, the position of the Interior Ministry within <b>the</b> <b>Palestinian</b> Security Services is unclear.|$|R
